Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL WORK TATSUKI FUJIMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(SERIALIZED IN\NSHUEISHA'S SHONEN JUMP+)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}It's that same dream again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's that same dream I always dream...\NAnd always forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Pochita] Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pochita!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pochita, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just in a dream right now.\NLet me pet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Pochita] Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[high-pitched ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted]\NDo not open the door. No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Power yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? You're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still in a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[cat yowls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I get all this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji strains] So this isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,["Iris Out" playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,CHAINSAW MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,PUBLIC SAFETY DEVIL HUNTERS\NLARGE-SCALE ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[no audible dialogue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ONE MOMENT PLEASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,CHAINSAW MAN - THE MOVIE:\NREZE ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DEVIL HUNTER TOKYO HQ BUILDING
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Power, you drank too much blood,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you drank too much blood
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- in that fight against the zombies.\N- [yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- We've got to drain some blood out of you.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Drain her blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Power has to have her blood drained\Nevery once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or else she becomes even more scary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- and self-centered than she normally is.\N- [yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Makima] So that's why... Denji...\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I borrow Power for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As for who's going to be your new buddy\Nwhile I'm borrowing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy said\Nhe wants to team up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw! Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] He's the Shark Fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, he's so ferocious that no one\Ncan even have a conversation with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said that as long as he gets\Nto pair up with you, Denji,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- he'll do whatever you tell him to.\N- He'll do whatever I tell him to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- How come?\N- I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because your faces look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw! I'll do whatever you say!\NNo matter what! Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best! You're the greatest!\NLord Chainsaw! You're the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me! I'm not into men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You look unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are feeling great,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then how about going on a date\Nwith me tomorrow on our day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] Huh? Denji, you're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an hour early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so cute! She's so cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, what time did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep last night.\NI got here at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what's the plan for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never hung out with a girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, from now until midnight,\Nwe're going to go movie-theater hopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[action music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting, exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- [characters grunting]\N- [weapon slashes]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji]\N{\i1}Well, this isn't what I was expecting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Everyone's laughing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't that funny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [blows landing]\N- [characters grunting, exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makima's not laughing either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima]\NIt wasn't very interesting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like they spent a lot of money\Nmaking that movie though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... let's go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[somber music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[viewers sniffling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Everyone's crying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not crying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] I didn't like how it felt\Nwhen they were trying to force us to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[classical music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the music was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- [creature growls]\N- [character shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The story seemed so fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just average.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The next movie is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,CINEMA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says this movie\Nis hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try watching it, Denji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Honestly, all the movies\Nwe've seen today are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I don't get movies or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I only find one good movie\Nfor every ten movies I watch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But one of those\Nwas a movie that changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- [birds chirping]\N- [footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[slow piano music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Huh? Whoa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This scene isn't even that important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope Makima doesn't see me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to forget that last scene\Nuntil the day I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That last movie made\Nthe price of the ticket worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Makima, do you think I have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[heartbeat thumping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that I felt butterflies\Nmeans that I do have a heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[fundraisers] Donations, please!\NDonations, please! Donations, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're collecting donations for children\Nwho've been victimized by devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Donations, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a heart,\Nso I can even make a donation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[fundraiser] Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving away flowers\Nto everyone who makes a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[fundraiser] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the fact that\NI can feel that the flower is beautiful{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}also means I have a heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[fundraisers] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Makima, you're incredible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel so much better\Nafter talking to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makima said that once I've gathered\Nall the pieces of the Gun Devil's flesh,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she'll grant me one wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case... I think I want\Nto ask her to be my girlfriend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever I have a free moment,\NI always start thinking about Makima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've squeezed other girls' boobs\Nand kissed other girls before too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my heart belongs completely to Makima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I'm going\Nto fall for anyone else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam! You stay hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone sees you, I won't be able\Nto walk around in public anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do fiends all have such weird names?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- [door opens]\N- [Denji sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have brought an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[liquid shaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Whoa! [giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- [door opens]\N- [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather report said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? [laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[person crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Huh? How come you're crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,looks like my dog that passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're saying I'm a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gags]\N- Hmm? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [retches]\N- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I've got a handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no trick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[gentle music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. It stopped raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I work at a café called Crossroads\Nright down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drop by,\NI'll pay you back for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you come, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.\NI'm going to deduct it from your pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this water to table four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stingy! Stingy! Stingy! Stingy! Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You got here faster than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came so that you could pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh.\N- Let's have a drink together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can you bring some coffee\Nfor me and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We only get customers\Nin the morning anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[person]\NA cup of coffee is my gift back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] What's with that face?\NYou're just pretending you're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee tastes bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes like it's from the gutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}She's touching me a lot,\Nand she's laughing at my jokes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she likes me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Reze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, I've never met someone\Nas interesting as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammers] Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure about it now. She does like me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I like people who like me too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makima... help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to start falling for this girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had three already. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go on patrol now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating ice cream made me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that eating takes energy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to work anymore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki]\NThey found out where the Gun Devil is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be an expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to participate, I need to have\Nmore experience defeating big devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to\Ngo look for more devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my buddy. Please help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I think about it a bit\Nafter I've had another ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell the leadership\Nthat you're useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to kill you as a devil.\NAre you sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] {\i1}He's the second-most\Npowerful member of Division 4,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after Captain Kishibe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least he would be\Nif he weren't always so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to join the expedition\Nto defeat the Gun Devil,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then you should try\Nto make good use of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] I don't think\NI can get along well with a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you get along with Power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a fistfight just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just use him for your own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's someone\Nwho killed every single person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in the village where he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to put it more accurately:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He sucked the lifespans out of them\Nand transformed them into weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] He has the power to transform the\Nlife of anyone he touches into a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That katana you have\Nis one of his weapons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those weapons can do things like cut\Nthrough ghosts that no one can touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and have different special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you have to pretend.\NJust be friendly with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[crows cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've eliminated the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure\Nnot to touch its blood or its flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be a private Devil Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was being eaten up by this devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower half of his body\Nis gone already. He's almost dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[sputtering]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me. Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Your power gives you\Nthe ability to kill him painlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Grant him his wish to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be an angel, but I'm also a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that humans\Nshould suffer when they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[person gasps, sputtering]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[sputtering stops]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can become friends.\NEven if I pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Makima's the one\Nwho found my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's why my heart belongs to Makima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... my body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's moving on its own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The food here's not that good. No one\Nwould come every day for a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have such bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some curry and some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And some fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you come eat\Nover here at this table?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're studying right now, right?\NEven though you're on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't go to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working as a Devil Hunter\Ninstead of going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.42,0:24:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to study over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [stammers]\N- Scoot over! Scoot over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.01,0:24:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[food sizzling]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn how to read kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] You can't read kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.73,0:24:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.23,0:24:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.28,0:24:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.24,0:24:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji]\NThat says "balls," you sex-crazed girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.78,0:24:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Balls" is the only one I can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.37,0:24:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.38,0:25:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have\Ngone to school with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.51,0:25:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.01,0:25:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.89,0:25:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}What am I saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.02,0:25:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- Do you want to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- At night.\N- At night?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go explore\Na school building together at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.91,0:25:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.95,0:25:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart belongs to Makima,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my body won't listen to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.13,0:25:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[water running]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.05,0:25:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.05,0:25:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon] What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:26:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[person]\NWhy do you devils want Chainsaw's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.94,0:26:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon] You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you need to focus on\Nis holding up your end of the contract
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.28,0:26:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[person chuckles] Sounds like we're\Ngoing to be working together for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get more comfortable\Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Typhoon Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The contract is that once\NI get my hands on Chainsaw's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.50,0:26:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll let me use your powers forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon] Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.38,0:26:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The human who has Chainsaw's heart\Nhas killed lots of devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.93,0:26:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because\Nthe devils aren't very bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed a Devil Hunter from China\Nfor a job once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.36,0:26:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a merciless Devil Hunter.\NThey said he had no blood or tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.49,0:26:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Typhoon] How did you kill him?\N- [thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.41,0:26:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked for how I could\Nmake him bleed and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.25,0:27:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I took his wife and kid as hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.09,0:27:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I skinned them\Nand showed him their hides.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He let me kill him after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.22,0:27:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[blade scrapes]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.55,0:27:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- [blade stabbing]\N- [screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Denji, aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Uh, I'm not really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.20,0:27:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This just feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.37,0:27:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze giggles] What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.92,0:27:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I'm a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.46,0:27:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.55,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Makima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.10,0:28:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest,\NI don't want to hold her hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.69,0:28:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my body just...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.81,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.15,0:28:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.70,0:28:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Two! It's two!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.66,0:28:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.58,0:28:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- What does this English word mean?\N- I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.33,0:28:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is: "Big ass."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.87,0:28:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You sex-crazed girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.46,0:28:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... So this is what school is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.55,0:28:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got the hang of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.84,0:28:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, is it really true that\Nyou didn't even go to elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.22,0:28:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.39,0:28:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that... bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.23,0:28:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.31,0:28:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.57,0:28:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A 16-year-old is still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you'd study for entrance exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.12,0:29:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,join school clubs,\Nand go out with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.37,0:29:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you... you kill devils\Nand almost get yourself killed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.21,0:29:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Public Safety,\Nthat place you work at now,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.54,0:29:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is it really a good place?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.88,0:29:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a really good place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.34,0:29:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to eat three meals a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.14,0:29:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get to sleep on a futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.68,0:29:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the bare minimum\Nfor everyone in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.52,0:29:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that's normal for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's getting hot\Nfrom thinking too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.41,0:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to cool down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.37,0:29:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[calm music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.79,0:29:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggling] It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.64,0:30:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] I don't know\Nhow to swim that well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.65,0:30:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.69,0:30:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll teach you how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.82,0:30:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.41,0:30:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? [gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.41,0:30:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.29,0:30:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your clothes.\NYour clothes are going to pull you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.71,0:30:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] You're so sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.71,0:30:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to learn how to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.13,0:30:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am starting to want to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.68,0:30:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.31,0:30:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, you should get naked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dark. I can't see anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.56,0:30:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Calm down!{\i0}\N- {\i1}I can see everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.48,0:30:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my first time seeing nipples!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.77,0:31:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I take off my clothes now,\NI'll be betraying Makima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.53,0:31:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.95,0:31:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.33,0:31:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.91,0:31:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.08,0:31:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come over here, Denji!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.34,0:31:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Denji.\NIf I go, then my heart will go too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.51,0:31:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] I know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.76,0:31:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared to get in the pool\Nbecause you can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.89,0:31:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.47,0:31:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! It feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.68,0:31:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.94,0:31:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.44,0:31:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.90,0:31:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.28,0:31:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[classical music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[music fades]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.67,0:32:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.30,0:32:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.68,0:32:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.31,0:32:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.94,0:33:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you things you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.31,0:33:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things you don't know how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.94,0:33:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[splashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.37,0:33:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji! Breathe! Breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.00,0:33:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.26,0:33:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.84,0:33:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.22,0:33:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.10,0:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[both laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.85,0:33:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.98,0:33:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[both laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.74,0:33:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.74,0:33:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Reze] The rain's not stopping.\N- [Denji] Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Denji...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.88,0:34:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The country mouse or the city mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one would you rather be?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.51,0:34:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of Aesop's fables.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The country mouse lives a safe life,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.27,0:34:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but doesn't have delicious food\Nlike the city mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.61,0:34:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The city mouse can find good food,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's in danger of getting killed\Nby a cat or a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.04,0:34:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the country mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.66,0:34:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Makima captured me\Nand brought me to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.17,0:34:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart belongs in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.01,0:34:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to follow around a city mouse\Nlike you and put myself in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.22,0:35:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[no audible dialogue]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.52,0:35:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] I want to be the city mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.27,0:35:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the country mouse is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.94,0:35:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A peaceful life is what's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.15,0:35:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] The city has more good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.28,0:35:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.57,0:35:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze chuckles] Are you saying\Nyou just want to eat and have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.79,0:35:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.58,0:35:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, there's a festival\Ngoing on nearby tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.13,0:35:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go together?\NI'm sure it'll be fun. And delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.97,0:35:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go if it's after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.30,0:35:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.39,0:35:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.02,0:35:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.36,0:35:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so damn cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[feet splashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.63,0:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[metal scrapes]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Denji?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.52,0:37:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[person cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.60,0:37:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to go pee myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.07,0:37:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the bathroom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.59,0:37:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pochita.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have feelings\Nfor two different people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.97,0:37:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.81,0:37:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not talking about that angel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.14,0:37:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.81,0:37:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.27,0:37:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}The small girl has a pretty face,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she tried to kill me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.53,0:38:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[strains, panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.82,0:38:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.24,0:38:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}Power still tries to\Nkill me sometimes too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.58,0:38:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a narcissist, she's selfish,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.29,0:38:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's a pathological liar,\Nand she's a bigot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.84,0:38:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.84,0:38:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised you'd go\Nto the bathroom with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.51,0:38:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] {\i1}What am I going to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.93,0:38:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I close my eyes, there's two of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.19,0:38:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pochita. Which one would you choose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.94,0:38:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.75,0:39:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.30,0:39:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to pee on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.43,0:39:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.47,0:39:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.97,0:39:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.68,0:39:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you have any idea who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.35,0:39:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.65,0:39:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a piece of cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.32,0:39:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a piece of cheese\Nfor luring out the mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.95,0:39:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.12,0:39:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to skin your face,\Ncarve out your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.62,0:39:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and show it all to Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.41,0:39:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what I'm going to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your precious woman is still alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.88,0:39:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And whenever I do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.47,0:39:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone starts listening to me\Nfor some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.89,0:39:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all that's left\Nfor me to do is to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.93,0:39:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The only piece of your body I want\Nis your skin and your eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.19,0:39:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.65,0:40:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.20,0:40:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.58,0:40:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[in Russian]\N{\i1}♪ I have a date with Jane today ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.02,0:40:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ All is ready ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.98,0:40:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ In the morning\NWe'll go to church together ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We will drink coffee ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.16,0:40:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And eat omelets at a café ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.63,0:41:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ After a walk ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.30,0:41:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ In a park ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.05,0:41:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We will go to an aquarium ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.56,0:41:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we will see dolphins and penguins ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.90,0:41:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Loved by Jane ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We will rest after lunch ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.65,0:41:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ So, what did we do in the morning? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.79,0:41:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We will speak about it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.17,0:41:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Until we remember ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.46,0:41:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We won't remember ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.51,0:41:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we will sleep\NAt the church that night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.88,0:42:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who made the storm\Nto trap us inside the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.17,0:42:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon]\NI didn't know you were here, Lady Reze.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.47,0:42:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn a blind eye\Nto what you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.81,0:42:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, you'll obey me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.39,0:42:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go deal with his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.73,0:42:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[airplane passing overhead]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.91,0:43:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm.\N- [footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.37,0:43:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.76,0:43:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Boo!\N- Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.18,0:43:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.15,0:43:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.52,0:43:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[calm piano music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[no audible dialogue]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.51,0:44:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[music ends]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.10,0:44:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about this place\Nfrom the owner of the café I work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.02,0:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it's the best spot\Nto watch fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.19,0:44:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else ever comes here.\NIt's a secret spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.99,0:45:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.05,0:45:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Hey, Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.01,0:45:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.05,0:45:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your current situation is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.30,0:45:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only 16,\Nbut they're not letting you go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.31,0:45:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're making you kill devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.89,0:45:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something\Nthis country should allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.06,0:45:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.53,0:45:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you quit your job\Nand run away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.99,0:45:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.74,0:45:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you\Nfor the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.91,0:45:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.63,0:45:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.17,0:45:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.97,0:46:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend has a place\Nwhere Public Safety will never find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.43,0:46:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't happen right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.43,0:46:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can go to school\Ntogether there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.73,0:46:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do all that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.94,0:46:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.40,0:46:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.28,0:46:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you having\Nsuch a hard time deciding?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.54,0:46:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.79,0:46:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.46,0:46:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.04,0:46:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just recently started\Nto feel appreciated at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.71,0:46:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go farther away without supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.47,0:46:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gradually learning how to deal with\Nmy buddy, who has a shitty personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.81,0:46:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've finally started to become friends\Nwith my difficult senior colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.69,0:46:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've found a goal\Nto work towards at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.94,0:46:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are starting to get fun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.69,0:47:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I keep seeing you\Nwhile I continue to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.95,0:47:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- The fireworks are about to begin!\N- This way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.37,0:47:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.17,0:47:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.75,0:47:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.59,0:47:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone else you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.30,0:47:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.37,0:47:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[child exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.41,0:47:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.16,0:47:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.16,0:47:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[crowd chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.00,0:48:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[chattering increases]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.01,0:48:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[crunch]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.94,0:48:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.11,0:48:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.75,0:48:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.26,0:48:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.93,0:48:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.39,0:49:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, I'm going to take your heart. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.28,0:49:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.32,0:49:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.29,0:49:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam] Run away! Run away!\NWe're in trouble! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.96,0:49:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How come I didn't notice anything\Nfrom the smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.09,0:49:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's dangerous, Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.59,0:49:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.18,0:49:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Bomb Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.94,0:49:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.17,0:50:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.27,0:50:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.19,0:50:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[strains]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.20,0:50:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.41,0:50:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.87,0:50:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.00,0:50:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.63,0:50:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Are you from Division 4 too?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.30,0:50:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go if you leave Denji there\Nand leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.93,0:51:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.98,0:51:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.69,0:51:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.74,0:51:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.24,0:51:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.51,0:51:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I wanted to go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.47,0:51:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. She's killing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.64,0:51:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've encountered a devil\Nnear the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.14,0:51:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,2034.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.86,0:51:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.27,0:51:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you private Devil Hunters?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.69,0:51:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. She said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.78,0:51:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.89,0:52:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] They sure ran away fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.56,0:52:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DEVIL EXTERMINATION DIVISION 2\NFUCHŪ TRAINING FACILITY
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.32,0:52:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.44,0:52:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[referee] Match over!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.28,0:52:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.28,0:52:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.37,0:52:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Devil Hunter] Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.58,0:52:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.33,0:52:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say no to you, Nomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.42,0:52:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Really?\NThen come back to Division 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.72,0:52:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stories I hear about\Nthe Special Division sound so gory anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.34,0:53:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything goes well, I'm going\Nto become the sub-captain in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.51,0:53:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens,\NI'm going to invite you to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.89,0:53:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.57,0:53:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] {\i1}Hey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.23,0:53:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't told him\Nthat you'll be dead in five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.86,0:53:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.36,0:53:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.49,0:53:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.45,0:53:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.71,0:53:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.50,0:53:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to die soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.84,0:53:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm alive, I have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.55,0:53:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die,\NI won't have to work hard anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.22,0:53:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.30,0:53:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a contract\Nwith the Future Devil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.18,0:53:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try asking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.89,0:53:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask it when I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.94,0:53:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.73,0:53:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aki! Come downstairs! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.52,0:53:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.28,0:54:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nomo] He showed up at the entrance and\Nclaimed he's from the Special Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.24,0:54:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this fiend really on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.91,0:54:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.91,0:54:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a devil do this to Denji?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.25,0:54:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomb is coming... Bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.71,0:54:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's one of the Gun Devil's allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.30,0:54:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.30,0:54:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.68,0:54:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps, stammers]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.01,0:54:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.80,0:54:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I could kill you right here\Nif I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.52,0:54:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell you, they'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.56,0:54:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Makima.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.44,0:54:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Makima?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.94,0:54:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.56,0:54:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is! Bomb's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.49,0:54:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nomo] Hey, beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.49,0:54:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.00,0:54:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is a training facility\Nfor Devil Extermination Division 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.71,0:54:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Members of the public\Nare not allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.34,0:54:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.17,0:55:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.26,0:55:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Reze...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.30,0:55:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Reze?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.68,0:55:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.22,0:55:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being attacked by a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.56,0:55:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.56,0:55:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sure smiling a lot\Nfor someone under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.27,0:55:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nomo.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.23,0:55:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your friend with you\Nand stay in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.44,0:55:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.69,0:55:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact headquarters and the vice-captain.\NSummon all Division 2 members.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.61,0:55:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.16,0:55:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.99,0:55:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen that beauty\Nsomewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.29,0:55:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the right time\Nto try to pick up women.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.70,0:55:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.50,0:55:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true. There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.59,0:55:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.34,0:55:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.64,0:55:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato! Tanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.10,0:55:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to dinner\Nif you can kill that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.68,0:55:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume she's a human.\NHandle her like you would a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.35,0:55:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] I guess it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.06,0:55:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.90,0:56:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.74,0:56:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.33,0:56:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.50,0:56:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kato] We've caused mold to grow\Nin her heart and intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.67,0:56:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nomo]\NShe's throwing up blood. It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.25,0:56:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she drinks blood and regenerates,\Nthe mold's not going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.17,0:56:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.35,0:56:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.06,0:56:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.52,0:56:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kato] She inflicted damage to herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.90,0:56:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to grow mold on her brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.61,0:56:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only do it if the target's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.11,0:56:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.61,0:56:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Devil Hunters gasping, exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.41,0:56:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.54,0:56:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.08,0:56:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.83,0:56:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Devil Hunter 1 screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.42,0:57:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Devil Hunter 2]\NShe's a devil! A devil is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.84,0:57:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She went right!\NDon't let her get near Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.67,0:57:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomo! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.89,0:57:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.60,0:57:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.74,0:57:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is! There's the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.33,0:57:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.95,0:57:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki Ando,\Nrequesting permission to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.50,0:57:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[superior] Permission granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.50,0:57:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[alarm blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.34,0:57:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japan,\Ndo you need permission to fire a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.93,0:57:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nomo] Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.94,0:58:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] You're pretty stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.02,0:58:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a real sight for sore eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.45,0:58:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.45,0:58:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[person] Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.20,0:58:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts, whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.58,0:58:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.50,0:58:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.25,0:58:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.55,0:58:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- [Fox Devil] What's that taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.13,0:58:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- [Fox Devil] I hate this taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.47,0:58:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.85,0:58:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.27,0:58:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to go\Nto a singles mixer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.31,0:58:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nomo] Take me with you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.98,0:58:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive. You have them\Ndrink some of your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.36,0:58:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.95,0:58:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.20,0:59:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to start the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.46,0:59:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.46,0:59:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed me a future\NI didn't want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.38,0:59:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.46,0:59:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.39,0:59:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them to show you\Nhow powerful I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.14,0:59:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kill anyone if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.86,0:59:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Denji out of the car and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.86,0:59:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.24,0:59:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.29,0:59:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.96,0:59:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The gasoline is going to\Nmake that car burn to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.84,0:59:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.76,0:59:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.85,1:00:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the Special Division for backup.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.85,1:00:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They saved us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.32,1:00:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.74,1:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.66,1:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I kicked with everything I got just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.58,1:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Nice kick.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.75,1:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.54,1:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobeni! We're changing strategies!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.63,1:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.88,1:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a lot stronger than us!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.09,1:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a strategic retreat!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.97,1:00:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.72,1:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Kobeni whimpering]\N- [thuds]
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.68,1:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs... My legs...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.27,1:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs gave out...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.32,1:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs... My legs...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.40,1:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.11,1:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.12,1:01:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quit my job. So please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.70,1:01:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.52,1:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.85,1:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[static on radio]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.15,1:01:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Chainsaw's awake now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.90,1:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But the bomb girl's right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.99,1:01:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shit! Damn!\N- [music faintly playing over static]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.03,1:01:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmitter's broken on this car.\N[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.04,1:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[heavy metal music playing]
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.37,1:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this car?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.25,1:01:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes down to it,\NI'm going to crash this car into her!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.04,1:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let her have Denji!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.63,1:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- [Aki] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.38,1:02:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] He's cutting the top of the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.43,1:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.60,1:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Denji!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.89,1:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had that much blood yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.10,1:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] It hurt so much,\NI thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.23,1:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain's all mixed-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.32,1:02:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I spent some time\Nlooking back on what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.28,1:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just realized
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.20,1:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that every single girl I ever meet\Nalways tries to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.37,1:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone always wants Chainsaw's heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.12,1:02:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't anyone want Denji's heart? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.30,1:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do like you, Denji. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.05,1:02:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.05,1:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [horn honks]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.64,1:02:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to the enemy!\NYou're so gullible!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.22,1:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji sighs]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.27,1:02:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.\NI was about to get tricked.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.40,1:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.61,1:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.53,1:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Makima!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.41,1:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Makima?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.82,1:03:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji, I didn't know that witch\Nhas got you in the palm of her hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.45,1:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it would have been no use\Neven if we ran away together.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.58,1:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Aw.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.25,1:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I never kissed you! Aw.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.80,1:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone else dies because of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.13,1:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have trouble getting\Nout of bed in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.18,1:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.85,1:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Denji.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.85,1:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show you how we fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.60,1:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.48,1:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[music continues]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.99,1:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts, groans]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.17,1:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Denji. You're not applying\Nwhat you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.30,1:04:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just swing\Nyour chainsaws around.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.13,1:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to understand\Nyour own power better.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.93,1:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.68,1:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.03,1:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[chainsaws whirring]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.98,1:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[pedestrians scream]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.07,1:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[pedestrian whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.70,1:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Regeneration?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.03,1:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were revving the engine
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.62,1:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- before you got kicked.\N- [chainsaw whirs]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.24,1:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You Devil!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.72,1:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] {\i1}If I mess up even\Na single move, I'm going to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.64,1:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see the future,\Nbut only a few seconds in advance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.68,1:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if my body\Nwill be able to react in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.19,1:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[pedestrians screaming]
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.02,1:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect judgment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.95,1:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect judgment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.20,1:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect judgment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.79,1:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.68,1:06:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Galgali] That was close!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.89,1:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Aki gasps]\N- Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.47,1:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever\Nwanted to be friends with a Devil!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.06,1:07:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Galgali] Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.90,1:07:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Time-out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.07,1:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm anemic\Nand I'm almost naked over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.90,1:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got the two of you.\NThat's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.15,1:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Should we give her a break?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.66,1:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.03,1:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.16,1:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The time-out is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.75,1:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.59,1:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Reze! Typhoon is here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.97,1:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.48,1:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers, strains]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.90,1:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.82,1:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.20,1:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[kisses]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.00,1:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take your blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.79,1:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.39,1:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam stammering]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.14,1:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[chainsaw whirs]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.39,1:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.23,1:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal devil would have been dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.06,1:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so impressive, Lord Chainsaw!\NYou're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.11,1:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] Your girlfriend has killed\Ntoo many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.07,1:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let her run free,\Nthen many more will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.41,1:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chainsaw. Make your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.08,1:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either let her kill you\Nand minimize the damage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.08,1:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or kill her instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.04,1:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Well, that's an easy decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.42,1:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Reze is incredibly powerful, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.97,1:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] Shark, you know\Nabout the Chainsaw Devil, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.97,1:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die today,\Nthen you should tell us what you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.48,1:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw runs really fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.65,1:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he goes places,\Nhe doesn't just use his legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.49,1:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He uses the chains on his chainsaws\Nto get around.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.20,1:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He flings his chains through the air\Nand hooks them on buildings,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.08,1:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he swings\Nfrom building to building!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.12,1:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Samurai Sword\Ndraws his sword to get around.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.42,1:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And Reze uses explosions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.17,1:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to apply my own powers too!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.55,1:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw, you're a genius!\NLord Chainsaw, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.84,1:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I should use chains to get around!\NI see! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.31,1:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.10,1:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.98,1:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Beam! Turn into a shark!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.36,1:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.44,1:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.20,1:10:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use chains to control Beam,\Nand Beam is going to run like a horse!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.16,1:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[straining] That's not it...\NThat's not it...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.79,1:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.37,1:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're supposed to shoot out\Nthe chains from your arms
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.34,1:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and hook them onto buildings.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.00,1:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the right way! Right, Beam?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.76,1:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! You're right! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.01,1:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Run, Beam!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.43,1:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.61,1:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji cackling]
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.65,1:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze giggling] What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.28,1:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki] Denji!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.16,1:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.62,1:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji! I'm going to make you\Nregret coming back to life!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.58,1:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam! Don't make me regret this!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.79,1:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam] Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.30,1:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.80,1:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Galgali] It's a monster battle!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.22,1:11:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going to\Nhave to sit it out and watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.60,1:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.60,1:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.07,1:11:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep missing!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.07,1:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.86,1:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Denji cackles]\N- [Beam] I'm tired of the explosions!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.07,1:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.25,1:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasps]\N- [chainsaw whirring]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.09,1:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take that!\N- Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.22,1:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.51,1:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut off a beautiful woman's leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.18,1:11:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Reze! Take my blood!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.98,1:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Oh! Good!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.90,1:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's not good!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.86,1:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckling] This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.61,1:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[straining]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.50,1:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab on to something!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.79,1:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.39,1:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.97,1:12:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! You can let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.89,1:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to die, I don't care!\NIt just means today was my day to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.48,1:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.61,1:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been ready to die for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.15,1:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[straining]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.37,1:13:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [screams]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.80,1:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aki panting]
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.39,1:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Angel] Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.43,1:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you touch my hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.39,1:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you want to die?\N- Of course I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.77,1:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did my lifespan\Ndecrease just now?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.28,1:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.70,1:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to die,\Nthen die somewhere far away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.00,1:13:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore,\Nwatching someone die
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.75,1:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.44,1:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam] Lord Chainsaw!\NWe're in trouble! Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.57,1:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw-- [screams]
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.29,1:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Hmm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.20,1:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji cackling]
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.25,1:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.34,1:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.09,1:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[both exclaim]
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.89,1:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.12,1:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[chainsaw whirs]
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.25,1:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Whoa. [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.01,1:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] You were hanging in there\Nfor a pretty long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.60,1:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's time now...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.43,1:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.19,1:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.65,1:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.24,1:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] That was close!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.37,1:16:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.49,1:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw!\NI'll make sure you won't regret this!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.55,1:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Hey! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.26,1:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to turn the whole city\Ninto mincemeat at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.72,1:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam! We've got to get\Nthat fat-ass to shut up first!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.56,1:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.03,1:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Typhoon] I found you!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.78,1:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[chainsaws whir]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.95,1:17:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.08,1:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[baby crying]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.76,1:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.01,1:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.60,1:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackling]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.61,1:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.49,1:17:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam! Send me flying!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.99,1:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims] Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.41,1:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.50,1:17:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it easy for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.29,1:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do\Nis swing my chainsaws around...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.26,1:17:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.84,1:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.60,1:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.02,1:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Beam!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.31,1:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.48,1:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.86,1:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[chainsaws whirring]
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.50,1:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.92,1:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.63,1:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.55,1:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.67,1:19:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Beam!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.58,1:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Reze?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.67,1:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lord Chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.19,1:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.03,1:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.67,1:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.47,1:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[shouts]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.68,1:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.93,1:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.94,1:20:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.83,1:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts, groans]
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.96,1:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.90,1:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.49,1:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[strains]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.03,1:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.49,1:21:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me, Beam!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.12,1:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Beam mumbles]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.24,1:21:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji. Don't you think\Nit's about time you gave up?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.54,1:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.67,1:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.67,1:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind whistling]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.68,1:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.93,1:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.27,1:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being a huge pain in the ass.\NJust hurry up and die already.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.82,1:21:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should have just\Nkilled me when we first met!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.20,1:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.45,1:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.33,1:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have taught me how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.92,1:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Huh... You're going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.81,1:22:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.03,1:22:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Chains?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.42,1:22:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.80,1:22:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still explode when you're wet?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.65,1:24:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.96,1:24:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.46,1:24:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you resurrect me?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.25,1:24:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a great life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.67,1:24:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times\NI get beat up or die,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.68,1:25:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as I get to eat good food\Nthe next day, I can forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.73,1:25:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.19,1:25:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if I capture you and hand you over\Nto Public Safety,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.73,1:25:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel like I had a fish bone\Nstuck in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.82,1:25:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were living\Na good life every day,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.45,1:25:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it would feel bad, having something\Npoking the back of my throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.25,1:25:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] Do you think you would\Nstill say that if I killed you right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.75,1:25:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.63,1:25:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone's going to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.63,1:25:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'd rather be killed\Nby a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.60,1:25:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.35,1:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.15,1:25:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really still believe\Nthat I like you for real?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.36,1:26:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The look on my face when I met you,\Nand the way I blushed... It was all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.66,1:26:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just trained myself how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.66,1:26:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.04,1:26:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.75,1:26:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I took too much time before I fought you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.13,1:26:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run away now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.22,1:26:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Denji] Do you want to run away together?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.27,1:26:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.14,1:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fight too.\NYou'll have a better chance at escaping.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.23,1:26:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.98,1:26:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let me get away,\Nthat would make you complicit in murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.45,1:26:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.20,1:26:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.79,1:26:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I shouldn't,\Nbut I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.62,1:26:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I still like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.29,1:26:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.13,1:26:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did teach me how to swim. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.08,1:27:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- [crack]\N- [Denji groans]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.42,1:27:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.63,1:27:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] You should learn to be smarter.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.59,1:27:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Reze! Hey, Reze!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.18,1:27:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.85,1:27:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be waiting\Nat the café at lunch!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.36,1:27:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.15,1:28:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.19,1:28:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, Beam! My hand won't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.28,1:28:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rev up my engine!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.55,1:28:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.48,1:28:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[meows]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.03,1:28:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[meows]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.58,1:28:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kishibe] {\i1}There's a fairy tale\Nthat mothers in the Soviet Union tell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.96,1:28:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when scolding their children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.17,1:29:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The story says that there's a secret room\Nin the military's munitions storehouse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.55,1:29:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the secret room is filled\Nwith orphans.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.76,1:29:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids who live there\Ndon't have any freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.26,1:29:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not allowed to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.89,1:29:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're treated like objects.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.44,1:29:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the military uses their bodies\Nfor experiments until they die.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.02,1:29:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be just a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.07,1:29:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, a newspaper reported that\Nthat secret room really did exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.16,1:29:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An American journalist was the one\Nwho uncovered the story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.20,1:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was all over the news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.66,1:29:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They published photos\Nof the children who were there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.62,1:29:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the story soon disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.00,1:29:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl who lured Denji in\Nwas one of the kids from that room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.17,1:29:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,TYPHOON DEVIL DAMAGE RELIEF FUND
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.30,1:29:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUR SUPPORT AND COOPERATION\NARE APPRECIATED
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.92,1:29:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A fighter created by the Soviet Union\Nto serve their country.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.43,1:29:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're called guinea pigs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.90,1:30:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[announcer] {\i1}The Yamabiko train bound for\NSendai will soon depart from Platform 12.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.11,1:30:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next stop will be Ueno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.11,1:30:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[announcer 2] {\i1}The train will now depart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.49,1:30:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the Yamabiko train\Nbound for Sendai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.74,1:30:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train will now depart.\NDoors are closing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.37,1:30:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stand clear of the closing doors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.15,1:31:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima] Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.65,1:31:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.86,1:31:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the country mouse too.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.91,1:31:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my friends has a field\Nin the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.16,1:31:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I go there to help out my friend\Nevery year in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.29,1:31:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The field has mice hiding in the soil\Nthat damage the crops.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.92,1:31:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to exterminate the mice\Nbefore the fields get covered in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.64,1:32:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we dig up the fields and have the dogs\Nkill the mice hiding inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.31,1:32:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.35,1:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever I watch...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.36,1:32:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so comforted.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.61,1:32:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze winces]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.32,1:32:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Makima]\NThat's why I like the country mouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.24,1:32:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reze] {\i1}Why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.36,1:32:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder why I didn't kill you\Nthe first time we met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.16,1:33:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Denji, to be honest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.96,1:33:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never been to school either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.18,1:33:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to come with Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.77,1:33:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to make\NHayakawa kill a girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.31,1:33:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.52,1:33:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm an angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.12,1:33:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.04,1:33:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the city a good place?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.09,1:33:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,["Jane Doe" playing]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.53,1:37:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.37,1:37:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Denji. I've got to close the café now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.00,1:38:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was too cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.50,1:38:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was from a different world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.17,1:38:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll meet a girl\Nwho's perfect for you someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.10,1:38:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.02,1:38:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,RECOMMENDATIONS
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.66,1:38:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.54,1:38:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,P-P-P-Power!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.21,1:38:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.71,1:38:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back! I tracked you down\Nby following your scent. [sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.13,1:38:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tiny café!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.68,1:38:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.89,1:38:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.39,1:39:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. What are you doing with those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.10,1:39:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They would really suit me!\NGive them to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.20,1:39:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't eat them!\NThey're mine! You thief!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.54,1:39:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.59,1:39:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit them out right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.88,1:39:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Spit them out! Spit them out!\N- [chomping]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.72,1:39:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[rhythmic ticking]
